OL,3,CJohannes Radebe says West End debut is
OL,4,C'pinch me moment'
OL,6,FITV News Entertainment Reporter Rishi
OL,7,FDavda speaks to Johannes Radebe about
OL,8,Fhis role in Kinky Boots, Strictly Come
OL,9,FDancing and finally feeling accepted
OL,11,FThe genuinely heart-warming smile and
OL,12,Froom-filling laugh that come from
OL,13,FJohannes Radebe make it easy to
OL,14,Funderstand why he's such a fan
OL,15,Ffavourite on Strictly Come Dancing.
OL,17,FLast year, he took his sequins and
OL,18,Fsparkles to the stage as Lola in the
OL,19,Fmusical Kinky Boots, which toured the
OL,20,FUK.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
