OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773997501
OL,3,CJohannes Radebe says West End debut is
OL,4,C'pinch me moment'
OL,6,FNow, the show's found a home in the
OL,7,FWest End - at The London Coliseum -
OL,8,Fand Radebe can't quite believe it.
OL,10,F"Walking around St. Martin's Lane and
OL,11,Fseeing 'Kinky Boots' and my face
OL,12,Feverywhere, it's everything that a
OL,13,Fperformer could ever wish for," he
OL,14,Fsaid.
OL,16,F"For a township boy from South Africa,
OL,17,Fin Sasolburg, to experience beauty of
OL,18,Fthis magnitude, it's a pinch me
OL,19,Fmoment."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
