OL,3,CJohannes Radebe says West End debut is
OL,4,C'pinch me moment'
OL,6,FNow 38, the dancer and choreographer's
OL,7,Fchildhood presented him with countless
OL,8,Fchallenges in his pursuit of his
OL,9,Fpassion for performing.
OL,11,FGrowing up gay in a conservative, run-
OL,12,Fdown, rural area meant the star was
OL,13,Foften the victim of bullying.
OL,15,F"A lot of times I was told that 'you
OL,16,Fwon't amount to anything', that's what
OL,17,FI grew up with as a young man.
OL,19,F"So the fact that I'm where I am is
OL,20,Fpurely because of perseverance and
OL,21,Fresilience."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
