OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773997501
OL,3,CJohannes Radebe says West End debut is
OL,4,C'pinch me moment'
OL,6,FJohannes began his career as a dance
OL,7,Fteacher in Johannesburg, before
OL,8,Fspending many years dancing on cruise
OL,9,Fships.
OL,11,FIn 2014, he joined South Africa's
OL,12,Fversion of Strictly Come Dancing. Four
OL,13,Fyears later, he became a professional
OL,14,Fon the UK incarnation of the
OL,15,Fcompetition.
OL,17,FIt was on the British Strictly that he
OL,18,Ffelt accepted for the first time in
OL,19,Fhis life.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
