PN,31405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773997501
OL,3,CJohannes Radebe says West End debut is
OL,4,C'pinch me moment'
OL,6,F"They offered me a pair of heels," he
OL,7,Fremembers, as a glow appears on his
OL,8,Fface.
OL,10,F"They said 'Would you like to do this
OL,11,Fin front of the world? Because we know
OL,12,Fwho you are and we want to show the
OL,13,Fworld how fabulous you are.'
OL,15,F"I was so happy that I didn't have to
OL,16,Fplay a role when I was at work."
OL,18,FRadebe was part of the first same-sex
OL,19,Fdance on Strictly in 2019 and was one
OL,20,Fhalf of the show's first male pairing
OL,21,Fin 2021, alongside John Whaite.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
