OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773997501
OL,3,CJohannes Radebe says West End debut is
OL,4,C'pinch me moment'
OL,6,FJohannes Radebe stars in the London
OL,7,Fproduction of Kinky Boots.
OL,9,FHe's now back in heels for Kinky
OL,10,FBoots, which, for those who haven't
OL,11,Fseen the musical, centres on an
OL,12,Funlikely partnership between a shoe
OL,13,Fmaker and a drag queen.
OL,15,FJohannes recalls one experience during
OL,16,Fa show in Norwich last year: "A mother
OL,17,Fcame with her trans daughter. They
OL,18,Fstuck around until I left.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
