PN,31407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773997501
OL,3,CJohannes Radebe says West End debut is
OL,4,C'pinch me moment'
OL,6,F"The child couldn't stop crying, but
OL,7,Fthe mum just said 'thank you' because
OL,8,Fshe got to 'see' her child on that
OL,9,Fday."
OL,11,FThat was when he first felt that he
OL,12,Fwas "doing something with purpose".
OL,14,FStrictly Come Dancing is due back on
OL,15,Four screens later this year.
OL,17,FThere will be new hosts, after Tess
OL,18,FDaly and Claudia Winkleman stepped
OL,19,Fdown, plus there are rumours of a
OL,20,Fprofessional dancer shakeup.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
